name: Whispering Grove Wilderness
description: Whispering Grove Wilderness is an enchanting forest where the trees seem to whisper secrets to one another. A verdant tapestry of moss carpets the ground, and shafts of sunlight pierce through the dense canopy overhead, casting dappled light. The air is at once cool and refreshing, filled with the scents of pine and wildflowers. Hidden streams gurgle softly, and ancient runestones lie half-buried in the underbrush, hinting at a forgotten past.
